The '''Extolled''' was the new name for the lowest [[Yuuzhan Vong]] [[Yuuzhan Vong castes|caste]] known as the [[Shamed Ones]].

Even though they were considered to be extolled, some Yuuzhan Vong (especially the [[Warrior caste]]) still did not show them the new respect they had gained and treated them as untouchables.

